OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FCould the likely changes to STV News
OL,7,Feventually have implications for local
OL,8,Fadvertisers?
OL,10,FIt's a question which has not been
OL,11,Fdiscussed in the row surrounding the
OL,12,Fstation's plans.
OL,14,FOfcom is due to say in the next few
OL,15,Fweeks whether to allow STV to cut the
OL,16,Fseparate service for the old Grampian
OL,17,Fregion.
OL,19,FThe row over this change has been
OL,20,Fintense.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15302
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut STV also wants to cut the two
OL,7,Fcurrent sub-opts ` those for the areas
OL,8,Fserved by the Craigkelly transmitter
OL,9,Fwhich covers Edinburgh and the Angus
OL,10,Ftransmitter near Dundee.
OL,12,FWhatever might happen, there would seem
OL,13,Fto be little chance of a reprieve for
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FThe current proposal ` which Ofcom has
OL,17,Fsaid it is likely to approve ` would
OL,18,Fsee most news output go out across both
OL,19,FSTV's franchise areas.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15303
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut there'd be a 9 minute recorded
OL,7,Fsub-opt for the Grampian area during
OL,8,Fthe 6pm programme.
OL,10,FIn itself, this does not affect STV's
OL,11,Fservice to local advertisers. For about
OL,12,F25 years, it's had 4 micro-regions.
OL,13,FThey match the current news regions but
OL,14,Fpredate them.
OL,16,FSTV has, however, mentioned that it
OL,17,Fhopes to save on distribution costs if
OL,18,Fthe news changes go through.
OL,20,FAs the station uses gifted space on
OL,21,FFreeview, this surely refers to
OL,22,Fsatellite distribution.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15304
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FOnly one of STV's HD regions is on the
OL,7,Fgroup of multiplexes used by ITV 1. Its
OL,8,Fother three regions are on space hired
OL,9,Felsewhere.
OL,11,FIndeed the Dundee and Edinburgh HD
OL,12,Fregions are encrypted. Freesat viewers
OL,13,Fthere get an SD service on channel 103
OL,14,Fto ensure they get the correct local
OL,15,Fnews and ads.
OL,17,FWill this be sustainable if Ofcom
OL,18,Fapproves the cuts?
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15305
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FAre two extra HD slots worth it for
OL,7,Fadverts for Paulo's chip shop and the
OL,8,Findependent used tyre specialist? (Well
OL,9,Fmaybe that's unfair to the ultra local
OL,10,Fadvertisers but whenever I've watched
OL,11,Fthey can seem like adverts for the
OL,12,Fsmall shop right opposite the cinema.)
OL,14,FTwo HD streams would seem enough. And
OL,15,Fthey'd probably be enough to satisfy
OL,16,Fall the major Scottish advertisers.
OL,18,FThe SD streams which would be freed up
OL,19,Fcould be used to bring STV + 1 to
OL,20,Fsatellite. It is currently only on
OL,21,Fcable and Freeview.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15306
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FAnd would the two small advertising
OL,7,Fsub-regions be viable if they were only
OL,8,Fon Freeview?
OL,10,FSTV has said nothing to imply any
OL,11,Fchanges are likely soon. In any case,
OL,12,Fpresumably there are contracts to
OL,13,Fhonour.
OL,15,FBut let's keep an eye on this.
OL,17,FITV closed some advertising sub-regions
OL,18,Fyears ago. They now align exactly with
OL,19,Fits news regions.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,154,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15307
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F153A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe world is a very different place too
OL,7,Fto the one which existed when these
OL,8,Fsub-regions were created.
OL,10,FSTV's commitment to advertising
OL,11,Fsub-regions over the years is
OL,12,Fcommendable.
OL,14,FSmall local advertisers have popped up
OL,15,Fin slots during popular network shows.
OL,17,FIf you want to see local businesses get
OL,18,Fa chance to grow or support a circular
OL,19,Feconomy, these regions have merit.
OL,21,FBut will they still make sense should
OL,22,Fthe news changes happen?
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
